    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>Igitur noverit omnium fidelium nostrorum presentium scilicet hac futurorum
                        sagacitas quoniam ego <persName ref="#people/3002" key="#Princeps"
                            >Iordanus</persName> Dei gratia princeps una cum <rs key="#fidelisOf"
                            >fidele</rs> meo <persName key="#Witness #fidelisOf"><name
                                ref="Wilielmus">Wigelmo</name></persName>, pro amore omnipotentis
                        Dei et redemptione animarum nostrarum necnon et pro redemptione anime <rs
                            key="#parentOf">patris</rs> mei seu et <rs key="#parentOf">matris</rs>
                        mee, concedimus atque firmamus in <rs key="#Monasteries">monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/84">Sancti
                            Benedicti</orgName> quasque et ad omnium <persName
                            key="#Abbots #Personal_rank" ref="#people/2421">Desiderium</persName>
                        <rs key="#Personal_rank">venerabilem</rs> eiusdem sancti <rs
                            key="#Monasteries">cenobii</rs>
                        <rs key="#Abbots">abbatem</rs>
                        <rs key="#Coloni/tenants">septem homines cum filiis et filiabus eorum</rs>,
                        scilicet <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Marcus"
                            >Marcus</name></persName>, <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name
                                ref="Constabilis">Costabile</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Petrus Sclavu">Petrus
                            Sclavu</name></persName>, <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"><name
                                ref="Iohannes Agorose">Iohanne Agorose</name></persName>, <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants"><name ref="Iohannes de Monacha">Iohanne qui
                                dicitur de Monacha</name></persName> et <persName
                            key="#Coloni/tenants #siblingOf"><name ref="Petrus de Monacha"
                                >Petrus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#siblingOf">frater</rs> eius et <persName key="#Coloni/tenants"
                                ><name ref="Iohannes Capuanu">Iohanne Capuanu</name></persName>, ea
                        videlicet ratione ut nostris futurisque temporibus per hunc nostrum
                        firmissimum scriptum sanctum cenobium situs in <rs
                            key="#Villages/settlements">castro</rs>
                        <placeName ref="#places/109" key="#Villages/settlements">Casino</placeName>,
                        ubi nunc Deo auxiliante supradictus domus Desiderius venerabilis abbas
                        preest, perpetualiter habeat et possideat, ita scilicet ut illis septem
                        supradicti homines cum suis liberis nullam reclamationem partis nostre
                        habeant, videlicet ut nullus homo nullaque qualibet nostri principatus magna
                        vel parva persona prephatum sanctum monasterium seu predictum domnum
                        Desiderium venerabilem abbatem suisque successoribus de iam supradictis
                        hominibus disvestire, inquietare, molestare vel per aliqua placita fatigare
                        presumat. Siquis autem nefandissimus hoc agere presumpserit, sciat se
                        componere <rs key="#Penalty">aurei Bizanteos solidos CCCCC</rs>, medietatem
                        supradicto monasterio et medietatem camere nostre. Et ut hec nostra
                        concessio firmam et stabile permaneat, manu propria ea roboravi. Ego
                            <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/3002">Iordanus</persName>
                        princeps. Ego qui supra <persName key="#Witness #fidelisOf"><name
                                ref="Wilielmus">Guilielmus</name></persName>. Ego <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Iohannes Burrellu">Iohannes
                            Burrellu</name></persName>. Ego <persName key="#Witness"><name
                                ref="Landulfus">Landulfus</name></persName>. </ab>
                </div>
            </div>
